name: Jukebox Archive
description: The Jukebox Archive initiative intends to acquire exclusive ownership of Kanye West's first Grammy-nominated album, "Graduation." Marking the very first step in the development & implementation of Jukebox, a decentralized, open-source digital archive of the world's most legendary musical compositions, owned and governed by the community.
